IMA BEAST broke alertly, soon ceded the lead content to press from outside going two to three wide, put away the inside foe moving clear in upper stretch but was soon overtaken, faltered and faded. HAI BOBBI tossed the head at the start, chased from inside, moved out to the three path coming to the quarter pole, ran on evenly. GLORIANNIA settled at the back racing off the rail, angled ten wide in upper- to mid-stretch, finished quite strongly but far too late. MI CORAZON was about mid-pack racing mostly four to five wide, went evenly and made no bid. CINNAMON BITS was off the pace outside a rival two to three wide through the turn, came out further for the stretch run, failed to rally. CARA CARA moved forward inside to soon take the lead, set a pressured pace, came up empty. VERDEJO was ridden along early on the turn saving ground inside, failed to menace. HARD TO CAPTURE broke a step slowly, was outside at the back four to six wide through the turn, failed to threaten. COLLECT DATTT was at the back inside a foe but in the three to four path through the turn, failed to menace.
